node.title: Livestream: Deputy PM with rapid antigen test post-Cabinet update
node.description: The Deputy Prime Minister speaks at the Beehive.
node.content: ["This livestream is expected to start at 4pm.\u00a0", "Deputy Prime Minister Grant Robertson is holding the weekly post-Cabinet Beehive press conference, filling in for Prime Minister Jacinda Ardern who is finishing her isolation period.\u00a0", "The Prime Minister on Monday returned a negative COVID-19 test result after she was deemed a close contact and had to self-isolate. She is required to continue isolating until the end of Tuesday, February 1.\u00a0", "Robertson is expected to provide an update on COVID-19 rapid antigen tests.\u00a0", "Watch the livestream.\u00a0", "App users watch here.\u00a0"]
